## Application Runtime Data & Local secrets configuration
## ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local app configurations containing environment parameters
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json

# Local user secrets storage folder for development identity
.microsoft/usersecrets/

# ASP.NET Core Data Protection keys generated locally
~/.aspnet/DataProtection-Keys/

# Publish output directories (Standard compilation publishing folders)
Publish/
publish/

